{SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.wloob.com/2019/09/20190926024033-5d8c252173523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.wloob.com%2F2019%2F09%2F20190926024033-5d8c252173523.jpg&h=7880e3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.wloob.com/2019/09/20190926024033-5d8c252139f68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.wloob.com%2F2019%2F09%2F20190926024033-5d8c252139f68.jpg&h=cb8cf04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.wloob.com/2019/09/20190926024033-5d8c252104bad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.wloob.com%2F2019%2F09%2F20190926024033-5d8c252104bad.jpg&h=6ad705f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.wloob.com/2019/09/20190926024031-5d8c251f5d4b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.wloob.com%2F2019%2F09%2F20190926024031-5d8c251f5d4b5.jpg&h=b8094b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n潛規則橫行各國演藝圈！最近日本寫真女星川村雪繪（川村ゆきえ）在節目上自爆曾經做過「枕營業」（陪睡之意），而AKB48的前成員成瀬理沙上節目時，也無意之間洩漏這個枕營業的秘密，在演藝圈要成名，代價顯然比想像中的更高。<br />\n▼川村雪繪在節目上自爆曾為了獲得工作而陪睡。(圖／取自日本網路)<br />\n<br />\n川村雪繪是日本頗為有名的寫真女星，除了拍攝性感畫報以外，也曾經演出不少電影、舞台劇和廣告，可說是多才多藝。但她最近在東京電視台的節目預告中，訴說自己為了能夠得到工作，曾經做過「陪睡」一事。<br />\n▼性感女星難為！川村雪繪縱然才華洋溢，也難逃「潛規則」。(圖／取自日本網路)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 自爆「枕營業」！寫真女郎川村雪繪、前AKB都陪睡 | ETtoday星光雲 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/44850#ixzz6CyK3p2wR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F44850%23ixzz6CyK3p2wR&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=6bc4e40b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/44850#ixzz6CyK3p2wR</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"86aba9d3e7ef0cd934021b582049b3ec6fb68d89","tid":1861690,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:46:44.000Z","msg":"推上熱門：美孚人，今晚7點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861651</a><br 